8.count words

A word starts when:
The current character is not a space.
Either it is the first character of the string or the previous character is a space.

s="I love Python"
count=0
for i in range(len(s)):
    if s[i]!=" ":
        if i==0 or s[i-1]==" ":
         count+=1
print(count)

